DESC:
Ted finishes wrapping cables and tearing down the stage.

{FCYAN}TED: {BRIGHT}"I'm gettin' too old for this shit."{NORMAL}{FWHITE}

The bar is winding down for the night.

The smell of piss and shit from the hippies at the show tonight is overbearing.

{FCYAN}TED: {BRIGHT}"I swear I'm going to murder every hippy in the galaxy.
      Gotta finish this album first."{NORMAL}{FWHITE}

The faint odor of cannabis lingers from a stall. Ted kicks the door in to find
a startled hippy. Thinking quickly, the hippy offers a lit joint to Ted.

{FGREEN}HIPPY: {BRIGHT}"Wanna hit, dude?"{NORMAL}{FWHITE}

Ted sizes up the bartender. He's a large rotund individual from the planet
Zappa. Best not to try anything stupid with him.

{FCYAN}BONGO: {BRIGHT}"Whatchoo won' Ted?"{NORMAL}{FWHITE}

{FGREEN}TED: {BRIGHT}"Where'd Chaz and the band go?"{NORMAL}{FWHITE}

{FCYAN}BONGO: {BRIGHT}"Heh, they hitched a ride with some fancy-pants producer.
        They don' need you no more, Ted.
        You bes' buy somethin' or get the hell outta here"{NORMAL}{FWHITE}

Ted needs to listen to some tunes, so he walks over to the ratty Jukebox that's
probably been here for centuries.

There are 4 buttons, and a blinking slot with text that reads: {BRIGHT}{FGREEN}INSERT 5 FLOYDS{NORMAL}{FWHITE}
